<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Demographics and Geographical Distribution</h3>



<p>Discover the profile of Ripple investors and gain insights into who&#8217;s investing in XRP. Understanding the demographics and geographical distribution of Ripple investors can provide valuable information about the market sentiment surrounding XRP.</p>



